{"tid":1458001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"癱瘓機場真係無得輸","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:44:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T14:21:30.000Z","uid":72650,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b18abecf0ad47b76cdc9be69639d2adca3fbf446","tid":1458001,"uid":72650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"一日半日政府可以由你嚇你等你地自己走，如果機場日日都運作唔到呢？<br />\n<br />\n政府可以點？<br />\n<br />\n1. 武力清場<br />\n太大風險 係機場放tg開槍絕對係引起國際關注同制裁 幾萬人佢拉得幾多個 拉到唔通又告到咩<br />\n<br />\n2. 咩都唔做等你自己散水<br />\n機場黎架你估夏愨道咩，無可能由得個機場日日停<br />\n<br />\n3. 跪低認錯 回應訴求<br />\n而家既政府點睇都唔會咁做<br />\n<br />\n所以講真，癱瘓機場真係無得輸，當年泰國佔領機場就係一個好例子。"},{"pid":"35c4bbe40bb05879db56c36b7c879d3ddd33f173","tid":1458001,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"0dcc17328ab23da664a1da4f142b3daf76228f80","tid":1458001,"uid":42141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:47:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc602d03f661ee2f24aa4a6634db01a7c34bc855","tid":1458001,"uid":42141,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"而家係我中意搞就搞<br />\n政府要硬食<br />\n<br />\n真正be water<br />\n<br />\n我地先係莊"},{"pid":"1217be84c370d3b9faa73c616cbf98a7932c4fd5","tid":1458001,"uid":72650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"佢真係無腦又癲到清場既話，我相信我們都是tank man"},{"pid":"07291661676fbb7e5a60eda68f8859571f54e650","tid":1458001,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70e1bdf95721214e5684519974c072b40e4d6ba8","tid":1458001,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"4 搵換衫黑鬼搞事<br />\n<br />\n名正言順清場 禁區出實彈<br />\n<br />\n今日下晝空穴來風 只係有旅客濟留先無出事"},{"pid":"b9bace99f50cc0bf418404694e19942e0b5d2928","tid":1458001,"uid":157653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:53:11.